          "className": "language-text"
        }}>{`subscriptions-transport-ws`}</code>{` to make your transition from Apollo Server 2 to Apollo Server 3 as easy as possible, but we recommend that you then migrate from `}<code parentName="p" {...{
          "className": "language-text"
        }}>{`subscriptions-transport-ws`}</code>{` to `}<code parentName="p" {...{
