        "className": "language-text"
      }}>{`your-graph-id`}</code>{`.`}</p>
    <p>{`In Apollo Server 3, you should instead specify your Studio graph ID explicitly when using features that connect to Studio. You can specify the graph ID by itself in the `}<code parentName="p" {...{
        "className": "language-text"
