        "className": "language-text"
      }}>{`new ApolloServer({apollo: {graphId}}))`}</code>{`, or alongside the variant in a string like `}<code parentName="p" {...{
        "className": "language-text"
      }}>{`your-graph-id@your-graph-variant`}</code>{` in the `}<code parentName="p" {...{
        "className": "language-text"
      }}>{`APOLLO_GRAPH_REF`}</code>{` environment variable (or via `}<code parentName="p" {...{
        "className": "language-text"
