        "className": "language-text"
      }}>{`lib.dom.d.ts`}</code>{` — e.g., `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "https://github.com/microsoft/TypeScript/blob/3c604f1c0a412ef41f58c3f9b239b25e8d725751/lib/lib.dom.d.ts#L1470"
